column2:
Cash receipts by selected commodity, 1910-2021F
Nominal (current dollars)

Footnotes
Data as of February 5, 2021
F = Forecast values.
'NA' indicates that commodity survey data is not available, and the value, if any, is instead included in either the 'all other crops' or 'miscellaneous animals and products' category, depending on the commodity type.
Values are rounded to the nearest thousand. When 'Real (2021 dollars)' is selected, nominal values are adjusted for inflation using the chain-type GDP deflator, base year=2021.
USDA/ERS Farm Income and Wealth Statistics
